Comment: 10,0:02:19.30,0:02:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Comment: 10,0:02:21.27,0:02:28.75,Default,,15,15,0,,But discovering the seven Words may shed some light on why Chariot du Nord disappeared...
