Comment: 10,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we gotta go.
Comment: 10,0:02:33.07,0:02:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But Professor Ursula...
Comment: 10,0:02:34.64,0:02:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 10,0:02:35.64,0:02:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, let's go!
Comment: 10,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Amanda!
Comment: 10,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Comment: 10,0:02:41.62,0:02:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Appleton is famous for its disdain of witches.
Comment: 10,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary Holy Grail...
