Comment: 10,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Metamorphie Vestesse! {uesutesu}{## making it -esse like faciesse, also cf. (trans)vestite with the clothing, even though faciesse is technically a verb in my setup, so... whatever}
