Comment: 10,0:05:33.25,0:05:38.80,Default,,15,15,0,,{\an8}Who do those foreign supporters think they are? Just wait until we put the thumbscrews on you when we next meet.{## you're not a sportsball guy, huh}
Comment: 10,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our honor is on the line with tonight's kickoff.
Comment: 10,0:05:42.16,0:05:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether in soccer or politics, we'll crush\Nthem and silence their nation for good.{## i'm soooo having a hard time letting a brit use "soccer".}
Comment: 10,0:05:47.48,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As I always say, our Prime Minister is just too soft.
Comment: 10,0:05:51.40,0:05:55.13,Default,,15,15,0,,He values compromise? What our country truly needs is...{## this is getting too real for me}
Comment: 10,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong statesmen!
