Comment: 10,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Father.
Comment: 10,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Chairman here!
Comment: 10,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chairman.
Comment: 10,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops, my bad.
Comment: 10,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recognize you. What class are you in?
Comment: 10,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? I can't recall.
Comment: 10,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude?!
Comment: 10,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Comment: 10,0:06:22.14,0:06:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you speaking to me like that knowing I'm Louis Blackwell? {##}
Comment: 10,0:06:25.14,0:06:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I'd even know you!
Comment: 10,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Color me surprised, then.
Comment: 10,0:06:29.09,0:06:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected to find a student at Appleton lacking respect for a Blackwell.
Comment: 10,0:06:34.31,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is the Chairman and this country's Minister of Defense!
Comment: 10,0:06:38.52,0:06:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? You'll have to excuse my rudeness! {##}
Comment: 10,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off!
Comment: 10,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Comment: 10,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanda, settle down!
Comment: 10,0:06:50.75,0:06:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What've you got there? Show me.
Comment: 10,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Squeak.
Comment: 10,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A rat! There was still a rat! {the posters say rat later on}
Comment: 10,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The familiar exterminator was supposed to eradicate them all!
Comment: 10,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Familiar exterminator?
Comment: 10,0:07:04.74,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats are the witches' familiars! Their underlings!
Comment: 10,0:07:07.36,0:07:13.78,Default,,15,15,0,,We had them all eliminated in order to prevent the deception \Nand corruption of witches in our holy place of learning!{## better word for "deceiving"?}
Comment: 10,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda school is this?
Comment: 10,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over!
Comment: 10,0:07:16.82,0:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you expect an obedient "Yes, of course!" from me, right?
Comment: 10,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Louis?
Comment: 10,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a familiar!
Comment: 10,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, are you serious?
Comment: 10,0:07:29.79,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an ordinary rat, no more than fodder for foxes if you threw it in a field.
Comment: 10,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let it outside.
Comment: 10,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I presume you take no issue? {or just "Problem?" for short}{## the short version wouldn't do his tone justice at all}
Comment: 10,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, pompous prick.
Comment: 10,0:07:44.79,0:07:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Comment: 10,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives us the honor of a visit from witches?
Comment: 10,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to try and start a fight?!
Comment: 10,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I've been able to look for the Word then? {singulasr}
Comment: 10,0:07:53.98,0:07:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut it! I don't give a rat's ass about the Words.
Comment: 10,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why'd you even come?
Comment: 10,0:07:59.86,0:08:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go out with a bang\Nbefore I quit Luna Nova.
Comment: 10,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so selfish!
Comment: 10,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what of it? I'll do what I want.
Comment: 10,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on your own too.
Comment: 10,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with you?
Comment: 10,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should at least ask.
Comment: 10,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Comment: 10,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to find a Word.
Comment: 10,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are seven ancient Words that make up a spell,
Comment: 10,0:08:21.26,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to find Chariot along with them.
Comment: 10,0:08:24.38,0:08:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You still admire that witch?
Comment: 10,0:08:27.47,0:08:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously! Becoming a witch who can give people\Ndreams like she did means everything to me!{## not sure what was up with the original line}
Comment: 10,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though nobody wishes that of you?
Comment: 10,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure, maybe nobody wants me to do it...{## hm? TLC? feels unfinished in an unintended way}
Comment: 10,0:08:40.63,0:08:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot understand why you'd go to such lengths when nobody ever asked you to.
Comment: 10,0:08:45.03,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I {\fax-0.2}want{\i0} to do it! Aren't you the same?
Comment: 10,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you before?
Comment: 10,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a certain conduct expected of a Hanbridge.
Comment: 10,0:08:54.85,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone around me expects me to become a great leader of this country.
Comment: 10,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a responsibility to answer them.
Comment: 10,0:09:01.34,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on about expectations and responsibility,\Nbut is that really what you want to do?
Comment: 10,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is not about what you want.
Comment: 10,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The things I must do have already been decided.
Comment: 10,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is decided.
Comment: 10,0:09:13.64,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I fail or lose heart,\Nthis is something I decided for myself.
Comment: 10,0:09:18.32,0:09:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become someone who can make everyone laugh and fill their hearts with excitement, like Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if you're unable to fulfill your dream?
Comment: 10,0:09:26.64,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\fax-0.2}will{\i0} fulfill it!
Comment: 10,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never give up until I do!
Comment: 10,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have a favor to ask...
Comment: 10,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about the legendary Holy Grail?
Comment: 10,0:09:35.91,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I did, I have no obligation to tell you.
Comment: 10,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What good would it do to sow the seeds of disaster in a troublemaker...{## sow the seeds of disorder in a troublemaker? that doesn't really work/make sense, does it? TLC?}{my bad, I swear I typed chaos}
Comment: 10,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like... you...
Comment: 10,0:10:16.16,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Those...
Comment: 10,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}What are they?
Comment: 10,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Comment: 10,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary Holy Grail? Found it!
Comment: 10,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta tell Amanda!
