Comment: 10,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw through your bluff.
Comment: 10,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna cheat, you better learn from the best.
Comment: 10,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...! {hey, he returned the favor. also I can't believe this is a high school}{## you never played cards with your friends?}{they're literally in a gambling room though. in school}
Comment: 10,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want some? {fucking idiot}
