Comment: 10,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, I forgot Akko's still got the leyline router on her!
Comment: 10,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a witch!
Comment: 10,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder I didn't recognize you!
Comment: 10,0:11:56.10,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, goddammit! Let me go!
Comment: 10,0:12:03.08,0:12:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Comment: 10,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's coming off!
Comment: 10,0:12:09.51,0:12:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't feel right.\NDid something happen to Amanda?
Comment: 10,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Done, next is over here!
Comment: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}TRUY NÃ - SỐNG HOẶC CHẾT\NCON CHUỘT - THƯỞNG 150£
Comment: 10,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're busted! Amanda!
Comment: 10,0:12:25.58,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What motive brought you to Appleton?
Comment: 10,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Comment: 10,0:12:32.42,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll figure it out once we capture the rat.
Comment: 10,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ways of making you talk.
Comment: 10,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Don't get yourself caught, Akko.
Comment: 10,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanda! Are you okay?
Comment: 10,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to save you!
Comment: 10,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away, stupid!
Comment: 10,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you try to rescue me?
Comment: 10,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have more chances to escape!
Comment: 10,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin the witch trial.
Comment: 10,0:13:03.58,0:13:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The verdict is guilty and the punishment torture, of course.
Comment: 10,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a trial at all!
Comment: 10,0:13:13.43,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this how it's always been? Witches are meant to receive judgement.
Comment: 10,0:13:17.62,0:13:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Comment: 10,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Comment: 10,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, not that!
Comment: 10,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You seriously found the Holy Grail?
Comment: 10,0:13:24.64,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something you witches need?
Comment: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Hừ...
Comment: 10,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to break it!
Comment: 10,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Comment: 10,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Comment: 10,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Comment: 10,0:13:47.33,0:13:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to interfere, Andrew?!
Comment: 10,0:13:49.58,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Louis, I have no intention of criticizing your ideology.
Comment: 10,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, I cannot see you as a gentleman!
Comment: 10,0:13:56.42,0:13:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're simply passing judgement\Non the intruding witches!
Comment: 10,0:13:59.86,0:14:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,True, those girls trespassed on our campus.
Comment: 10,0:14:03.41,0:14:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't condone a violent punishment.
Comment: 10,0:14:06.04,0:14:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As respectable members of our renowned school,\Nwe have an established way to resolve conflicts.
Comment: 10,0:14:11.54,0:14:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then.
Comment: 10,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you up on it!
Comment: 10,0:14:18.66,0:14:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In the case of irreconcilable differences at our academy,
Comment: 10,0:14:22.16,0:14:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the two parties are allowed to engage in a fair duel\Nunder the watchful eyes of the knight statues.{## should we do something about the knight statue? Statue of the Knight? the Knight's Statue?}{actually, there are two of them}
Comment: 10,0:14:28.16,0:14:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a tradition that goes back to our very founding.
Comment: 10,0:14:30.92,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win, I will release both the rat and the Grail.{## you can kill the two "the" too, if you want}
Comment: 10,0:14:34.67,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you lose, both you and the rat will receive\Njudgement, and the Grail will be broken to bits.{## turns out "holy grail shatter" is a weed strain or something}{oh anime, you so silly}
Comment: 10,0:14:41.75,0:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanda, this might be the key to reviving a Word.
Comment: 10,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For real? It's one of your experiences?
Comment: 10,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Comment: 10,0:14:49.81,0:14:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you mumbling about? En garde!
Comment: 10,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin when this falls.
Comment: 10,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?!
Comment: 10,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell're you doing?!
Comment: 10,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't fall yet!
Comment: 10,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to fight a witch fair and square!
Comment: 10,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanda!
Comment: 10,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall!
Comment: 10,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Comment: 10,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not use some of your fabled magic?
Comment: 10,0:15:43.10,0:15:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd mean wasting it on a bastard like you!
Comment: 10,0:15:46.53,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A witch without magic is worth\Neven less than a commoner!{## am i just imagining things or is this proper stilted english syntax? getting a bit tired but i think this works grammatically and has adequate levels of pompous prick to it}
Comment: 10,0:15:50.91,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep babbling! I don't need to answer to you!
Comment: 10,0:15:56.38,0:15:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Comment: 10,0:16:02.59,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finished!
Comment: 10,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a winner, wouldn't you say?{I don't know, it could be snappier or a one liner}{## line i spent most time on, coming up with nothing real though. there's no call/term in fancing for winning a bout or a match, "game over" isn't good, idioms felt kinda forced}
Comment: 10,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Amanda, that was so cool!
Comment: 10,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this a good enough experience for the Word?
Comment: 10,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe. I dunno.
Comment: 10,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Comment: 10,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!{## appropriate!}
Comment: 10,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd give this...
Comment: 10,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think you're doing?!
Comment: 10,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To a witch!
Comment: 10,0:16:56.94,0:16:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Comment: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Hả?
Comment: 10,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened?
Comment: 10,0:17:14.37,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, is this supposed to be that Word magic?{## typo}
Comment: 10,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Comment: 10,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Comment: 10,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not a Word at all!
Comment: 10,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain what's going on!
Comment: 10,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me! This was {\fax-0.2}your{\i0} Holy Grail!
Comment: 10,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're breaking the rules here.
Comment: 10,0:18:29.28,0:18:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, if only I could use magic...
Comment: 10,0:18:33.74,0:18:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Comment: 10,0:18:39.37,0:18:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Comment: 10,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw man...
Comment: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Ôi trời...
Comment: 10,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I meant to do that!
Comment: 10,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Comment: 10,0:19:05.03,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew!{## hmmm}
Comment: 10,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this to Amanda!
Comment: 10,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanda!
Comment: 10,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch!
Comment: 10,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Comment: 10,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've got this...
Comment: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Đây rồi!
Comment: 10,0:19:29.72,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Comment: 10,0:19:44.69,0:19:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's those things again...
Comment: 10,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.{## jesus}
Comment: 10,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Comment: 10,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
Comment: 10,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanda!
Comment: 10,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the Grail, Akko.
Comment: 10,0:19:54.65,0:19:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that thing was related to a Word.
Comment: 10,0:19:57.12,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been a demon sealed inside it a long time ago or something.
Comment: 10,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Comment: 10,0:20:03.21,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Comment: 10,0:20:04.88,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks pretty bad...
Comment: 10,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Comment: 10,0:20:12.51,0:20:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Comment: 10,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A witch? So it was your doing!
Comment: 10,0:20:19.93,0:20:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Louis! Look what that witch has done to you!
Comment: 10,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture her at once!
Comment: 10,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Respond! Don't just stand there!
Comment: 10,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken.
Comment: 10,0:20:34.55,0:20:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew! Are you protecting the witch?
Comment: 10,0:20:37.79,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a Hanbridge, but how will you\Nexplain what's happened to my son?!
Comment: 10,0:20:42.73,0:20:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is indeed the case that this girl\Ntrespassed on our school grounds. {both times Andrew calls her a girl rather than a witch}{## i think that's significant enough to warrant an edit and deserve some emphasis; also you don't really trespass into as you trespass on, do you}
Comment: 10,0:20:46.54,0:20:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In response, Louis proposed to enact a cruel and unusual punishment.
Comment: 10,0:20:51.17,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As you are aware, parties in disagreement\Nmay face each other in this place.
Comment: 10,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They simply followed Appleton's tradition.
Comment: 10,0:20:58.89,0:21:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She ended up winning their duel.
Comment: 10,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you brainwashed by that witch?
Comment: 10,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't, Father.
Comment: 10,0:21:07.06,0:21:12.23,Default,,15,15,0,,Before I knew what came over me, the situation devolved\Ninto chaos and I found myself on the verge of death.
Comment: 10,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl saved my life.
Comment: 10,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all my fault!
Comment: 10,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?
Comment: 10,0:21:21.88,0:21:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the rest. You've finished\Nyour business here, haven't you?
Comment: 10,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going.
Comment: 10,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thanks for saving me.
Comment: 10,0:21:34.17,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, uh...
Comment: 10,0:21:35.88,0:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you get what you came for?
Comment: 10,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Comment: 10,0:21:48.85,0:21:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, about today... I'm sorry for all the crazy stuff I caused.
Comment: 10,0:21:53.47,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're actually feeling guilty for once. {remorse, regretful}
Comment: 10,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guess I am.
Comment: 10,0:21:56.66,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you feel refreshed too, now that you got to go wild!
Comment: 10,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say I don't! I sure don't get bored when you're around.
Comment: 10,0:22:02.60,0:22:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And it wouldn't be any fun without you around either, so don't even think of quitting!
Comment: 10,0:22:06.35,0:22:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't make any promises.
Comment: 10,0:22:08.06,0:22:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go on more adventures with you!
Comment: 10,0:22:10.63,0:22:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Comment: 10,0:22:13.05,0:22:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Comment: 10,0:22:25.55,0:22:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Case 622: Experiment complete.
